{
  "stem": "12053.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, when we lived in the-- when she'd won her scholarship, she had to travel by train every morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one train, a particular train, that could get her to school in Oldham, which was quite a few miles away from the village we lived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just a few minutes before the train left, which was right down at the bottom of our road, Uncle Billy would say, oh, fetch me some cigarettes or fetch me something from the little shop.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the poor child was absolutely in, in, in terror in case she would miss her train and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, they'd deprive us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, that was-- we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was another thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were really hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And specially, they took a great delight on our fast days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our Jewish calendar sent us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we observed-- observed as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't observe the festivals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I taught the children, you know, to, probably to read a little bit of Hebrew and some of the prayers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's one-- another thing I took with me, a siddur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's a prayer book.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was most precious to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we couldn't observe or keep anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But on the day, the day of Yom Kippur, when you fast in the evening, we were allowed our usual ration of two slices of bread.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we fasted the whole day after that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And next evening, we had the other two slices.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we didn't have anything that we'd missed out on, lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By that time, I was working in a cotton mill, which I enjoyed very much, I must say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It got me away from home, but things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
